room_title: Escape room "Spirit of Harlem" by Hoodwinked Escape in New York
room_description: Your late Uncle Audobon left you his inheritance – the Crown Jewels of Harlem. You must take a journey through his life in Harlem and experience stories told and untold as you find your way around the Mecca of Soul. Escape with Harlem’s Crown Jewels of the past – or get hoodwinked!
